      • DoubleBooleanCount

        public DoubleBooleanCount(double val,
                          boolean bol)
        Constructor for this type.
        Parameters:
        val - (Estimate of) probability that a given example is labelled by a particular label ( 0.0 <= val <= 1.0)
        bol - true if the example is labelled by the label and false otherwise

        The ramaining field count is set to 1 and represents the number of examples seen that have the same val and bol.
